Opening times
       The Villa Arson is open to the public during exhibition time,
       everyday except Tuesday, from 2pm to 6pm / 2pm to 7pm in July and
       August.
       Closed on January 1st, May 1st, December 24th, 25th and 31st.
       Bookshop is open on the same schedule.

Guided tours
       Informations, rates and reservation about guided tours in english,
       italian:
       servicedespublics@villa-arson.org
       tel. +33 (0)4 92 07 73 84.

Access
       Tramway Line 1, direction Henri Sappia, tram stop Le Ray.
       Buses n° 7 and 4, bus stop Deux avenues
       Highway A8: exit Nice Nord. From the Promenade des Anglais: follow
       Boulevard Gambetta, and then Boulevard de Cessole
       To learn more about Nice public transit : Lignes d’Azur
